Speaker 2: You missed me, so please leave a message, telephone number, and I'll get back with you.

Speaker 1: Good morning, Richard.

Speaker 2: This is Jimmy. I'm calling from Niagara.

Speaker 1: The reason for my call is I noticed that the doctor reached out to you about your medication to confirm that she wasn't taking any other medications and you haven't responded.

Speaker 2: She would have sent it to your email.

Speaker 1: So in order for them to ship out your Viagra, you need to respond back to that email as far as that's concerned.

Speaker 2: If you have any questions, you can give us a call at Viagra 1-800-700-4197.

Speaker 1: Thank you and have a great day.
